     C                     PARM WWPAGN    P@PAGE  2        PLASTIC PAGE NO.
     C                     PARM           P@DATE  80       DATE OF KANBAN PUB.
     C                     PARM           P@TIME  60       TIME OF KANBAN PUB.
     C*                   ( OUT )
